(813, 'ACUGTR', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Chorley Gaiter', 'Our Chorley gaiter packs away into a fabric carry pouch. The gaiter is elasticated for comfort, features a centre back zip with a Velcro secured placket covering, an adjustable calf, a boot lace hook and an under boot wired strap.&amp;bull; Ployester Outer&amp;bull; Zip Fastening With Velcro-secured Placket Covering&amp;bull; Elasticated For Improved Fit&amp;bull; Under Boot Wired Strap &amp;amp; Boot Lace Hook&amp;bull; Packs Away Into A Convenient Fabric Carry Pouch&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)', '34.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/h/chorley_gaiter.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
