(815, 'COMLS49', 'Combrook Collection > Combrook Ladies', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Long Skirt 49cm', 'Three New Tweed Colourways - Juniper, Heather &amp;amp; GorseThis popular skirt is from our Combrook ladies collection. Crafted from a pure wool tweed with a water repellent outer there&amp;rsquo;s no need to worry if you get caught in an unexpected shower.Available in a choice of country colours the skirt is fully lined with a striking contrast lining and there&amp;rsquo;s a cleverly concealed side zip.', '119.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_skirt_in_avocado_6_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
(816, 'CAMLBRK', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Skirts & Trousers', 'Cambridge Ladies Waterproof Breeks', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;Cambridge Ladies Breeks are a top quality pair of waterproof women\'s shooting breeks with all the features you would expect to ensure your comfort on your day\'s shooting.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Sizing Tip - We recommend that you order the next size up to what you would normally buy', '99.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_cambridge_ladies_waterproof_shooting_breek_in_olive_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
(817, 'RUTLFLD', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Rutland Ladies Tweed Waterproof Shooting Coat - Shooting Fit', 'New HerbTweed ColourwayOur best-selling Rutland Ladies Waterproof Membrane Shooting Coat is crafted in a wool blend to create a durable yet stylish coat that is ideal for wide range of country pursuits.  This smart, yet robust tweed shooting coat is designed to allow plenty of shoulder movement and has a gently elasticated waist to stop cold winds from entering.The waterproof and breathable membrane, waterproof finish and windbreaker cuffs will ensure that you are protected against all the elements mother nature will throw at you.', '199.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_rutland_ladies_waterproof_shooting_coat_in_lichen_9.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
(818, 'RUTLWST', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Rutland Ladies Wax & Tweed Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;The Alan Paine ladies Rutland waistcoat is perfect for those days and nights where a coat or jacket is not needed.', '149.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_shooting_tweed_vest_rutland.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
(819, 'LODGBRK', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Loden Mens Breeks', 'Our Loden Breeks offer you a smart and comfortable look, designed with the sporting gent in mind. These smart yet practical trousers have been crafted from 100% wool, tailored to a classic fit for added comfort and wearability.For added convenience these trousers features two side entry pockets and two flap secured back pockets, for simple storage of all your essentials. The side entry pockets have been finished with mock suede facing panels for added attention to detail; these trousers have been fully lined in cotton for further comfort and wearability.Finished with a Velcro adjusted hem with false buckle detail, as well as a water repellent outer meaning these trousers will carry you through your outdoor adventures with ease.', '154.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_loden_mens_breeks_in_olive_9.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:50', '2018-08-14 13:45:50'),
(820, 'LODGCAP', 'Mens > Hats & Caps', 'Loden Mens Flat Cap', 'Our&amp;nbsp;men\'s Loden Flat Cap offers you a classic look with added convenience and style, crafted from 100% wool for added comfort and wearability. This stylish yet practical cap offers you a waterproof and breathable membrane for added convenience. This cap also boasts added attention to detail of a contrasting luxurious gold lining giving you an added touch of style.', '44.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_loden_shooting_flat_cap.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(821, 'LODGCOT', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Loden Mens Field Coat - Shooting Fit', 'Our new innovative Loden Field Coat offers you a practical coat ideal for those who live life outdoors, enjoying everything country life has to offer.This field coat has been crafted to the our Alan Paine shooting fit, giving you plenty of room for movement. A high quality 100% wool jacket with a technical Teflon coating to give you a water resistant and breathable jacket, with inner storm cuffs ideal for the ever changing weather.For added convenience jacket boasts an array of pockets, including two secure cartridge pockets, hand warmer pocket, and two secure inside pockets giving you plenty of room for all your essentials. This coat also features drawstring waist adjuster and stud adjusting sleeve tabs for added comfort and wearability.With the added attention to detail of a contrasting luxurious gold lining with lightweight padding, giving you a stylish yet practical jacket which will carry you through this season and beyond with ease.', '334.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_loden_mens_coat_in_olive_10.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(822, 'LODGSHW', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Loden Mens Shooting Waistcoat - Shooting Fit', 'Our Loden Shooting Waistcoat is a high performance practical men\'s 100% wool waistcoat that has been designed to be worn as part of the Loden shooting range or can be worn alone because it&amp;rsquo;s been tailored to a shooting fit for added comfort and wearability.Made from warm pure wool with a water repellent outer and with mock suede shoulder patches, deep cartridge pockets and a side vent for ease of movement across the back.This classic looking shooting men\'s waistcoat has authentic looking leather buttons centre front to compliment the shoulder pads giving you a combination of style and comfort.', '184.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_loden_mens_shooting_waistcoat_11.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(823, 'DURGWCT', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Dunswell Mens Waterproof Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'The Dunswell Mens Waterproof Waistcoat is waterproof and breathable making it easy to enjoy all that county life has to offer.For added convenience this is waistcoat features an array of pockets and a waterproof centre zip, ideal for your much loved country activities. This practical waistcoat has been finished with a luxurious checked lining to give you added style and wearability, carrying you through this season and beyond with ease.Furthermore, we are so confident of its durability that each waistcoat comes with a two-year guarantee.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/d/u/dunswell_mens_waterproof_shooting_vest.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
