(831, '001U58', 'Mens > Knitwear > Jumpers > Cashmere Jumpers', 'Selkirk Cashmere Long Sleeve Saddle Vee Neck Jumper - Classic Fit', 'This luxuriously soft classic men\'s cashmere vee neck jumper with traditional saddle shoulder is the hallmark of every fine gentlemen\'s wardrobe. Looks great when paired with a pair of tailored trousers, or for a more casual style wear with dark denim.Rare and precious, cashmere is one of the world\'s most prized commodities. Here at Alan Paine we believe buying a pure cashmere jumper is an investment. Each Alan Paine Cashmere sweater is produced using only the finest fibre from pure bred Cashmere goats living in the remotest mountains of China and Mongolia. The hair is combed from the undercoat with each animal producing just 4oz of Cashmere per year!Please not this cashmere sweater is part of our Classic Fit range.&amp;nbsp;To ensure maximum comfort, all our Classic Fit styles are generously cut across the waist, designed with a relaxed, more-traditional fit. &amp;nbsp;', '270.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cashmere_sweater.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(832, '128S42', 'Mens > Knitwear > Jumpers > Merino Jumpers', 'Radstone Merino Wool Crew Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', 'Crafted from pure merino wool for an indulgently soft handle, the this crew neck jumper fuses contemporary style with unapologetic luxury.Each jumper has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.Our model is 6&amp;rsquo;2&amp;rdquo; and wears a UK size 42&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 100% Merino Wool&amp;bull; Crew Neck&amp;bull; Short Sleeve&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Updated Fit - Our most regular &amp;amp; modern fit&amp;nbsp;(see Size Guide below for more details and Euro/US conversion).&amp;nbsp;', '80.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_merino_wool_jumper_crew_neck.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
