(840, 'AYLLJKTX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Aylsham Ladies Fleece Jacket Classic Fit - Clearance Colours', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;If you&amp;rsquo;re looking for a versatile fleece jacket then look no further! The Aylsham fleece jacket is perfect for warmer days worn over a shirt or ideal as an extra layer underneath a coat.The jacket has a robust front zipper, elasticated cuffs and two handy zipped pockets. The waist can be adjusted to ensure a snug, comfortable fit.Contrast piping around the collar and either side of the zip is a stylish addition.', '99.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/y/aylsham_ladies_fleece_jacket_brown_2.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
