(843, '096A19', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Honley Cotton Cashmere Cable & Bar Crew Neck - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Our Cotton Cashmere Cable Crew Sweater, features allover classic cabling, ribbing on the cuffs and hem. Easy to dress up or down, it looks just as smart paired with jeans and sneakers as it does with trousers and loafers.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced &amp;ndash; and the mitre of the &amp;ldquo;Crew&amp;rdquo; neck is closed by hand to give a perfect finish.', '104.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cotton_cashmere_cable_crew_neck_steel_blue_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
