(846, '196A24', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Kelby Cotton Cashmere Vee Neck Jumper - Trim Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;This cotton cashmere vee neck is a timeless wardrobe essential which can be worn with a pair of jeans or chinos.Crafted from a luxurious blend of Pima cotton and cashmere this plain knit vee neck is part of our trim fit range. Our trim fit range is more body fitting and also allows garments to be worn easily under jackets &amp;amp; layer on top.', '81.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cotton_cashmere_vee_neck_jumper_dark_navy_1_7.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
