(848, '196C23', 'Mens > Knitwear > Slipovers', 'Oakridge Cotton Cashmere Vee Neck Waistcoat - Trim Fit', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Trim Fit&amp;bull; 92% Cotton | 8 % Cashmere&amp;bull; 12g&amp;bull; Collar Style: Vee Neck &amp;bull; Hand Wash Only&amp;bull; Sleeveless&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)&amp;nbsp;', '75.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/o/a/oakridge_cotton_cashmere_vee_neck_waistcoat_dark_navy.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(849, 'ALEGSHT', 'Mens > Shirts', 'Aylesbury Mens Country Check Shirt - Classic Fit', 'A classic cotton check shirt is an absolute must for both on and off the field and we have just the shirt for you! This year we introduce a new classic fit country shirt to our Alan Paine Country Collection.&amp;nbsp;Due to the popular demand of our Ilkley Shooting Fit shirts we have introduced a more fitted garment this year. Ideal to sit under your gilet or country jumper.', '44.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_aylesbury_mens_shirt_in_chk39_gazelle.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(850, 'BERGCOT', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Berwick Mens Waterproof Shooting Coat - Shooting Fit', '&amp;nbsp;THE SHOOTING INDUSTRY 2017 FINALIST&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Our Berwick Men&amp;rsquo;s Waterproof Coat is the perfect addition to your countrywear this season and beyond, offering you a waterproof and breathable jacket you are sure to love! This jacket is perfect for getting you out into the countryside whatever the weather may bring, featuring an interactive zip to accommodate the Alan Paine Aylsham Fleece Waistcoat ideal for those colder days.', '224.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_mens_waterproof_coat_10.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(851, 'BERLCOT', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Berwick Ladies Waterproof Shooting Coat - Shooting Fit', 'Our Berwick Ladies Waterproof Shooting Coat is traditional looking women\'s shooting coat with all the functionality needed for successful day out shooting or stalking. This tough durable Cotton Polyester coat has a robust waterproof breathable membrane which allows perspiration to escape and prevents wind and rain to enter. This feminine coat is packed full of features including a map pocket, large cartridge pockets with drain holes and retainer straps from the hand-warmer pockets, and an adjustable drawcord waist which makes this coat fitted and flattering.', '219.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/b/e/berwick_ladies_waterproof_breeks_olive_1_.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(852, 'CAMKBRK', 'Childrens Clothing > Breeks', 'Cambridge Childrens Waterproof Country Breeks', 'Our Cambridge Childrens Waterproof Breeks are waterproof and breathable, complete with a water repellent outer fabric. The breeks are full lined with a mesh lining and include a zipped fly, two useful side pockets and two zip secured back pockets. Include a buckle adjustavle hem for comfortable and the perfect fit. These childrens waterproof breeks are suitable for both boys &amp;amp; girls.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Waterproof &amp;amp; Breathable Outer&amp;bull; Water Repellent Outer&amp;bull; Fully Lined With A Mesh Lining&amp;bull; Zipped Fly&amp;bull; Two Side Pockets&amp;bull; Two Zip Secure Back Pockets&amp;bull; Buckle Adjustable Hem&amp;bull; Outer: 100% Polyester Moss Suede&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Looking to complete the look? You can view our full range of children\'s country &amp;amp; shooting clothing here.&amp;nbsp;', '69.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/a/cambridge_childrens_waterproof_shooting_breeks_in_oak.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(853, 'COMBCAP', 'Combrook Collection > Compton Mens', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Country Baseball Cap', 'New Woodland Tweed ColourwayAvailable within a number of classic country tweed styles the Combrook Mens Tweed Country Baseball Cap is ideal for the modern man who spends his time in the countryside. The cap is lined in cotton and has a velcro strap at the back of the head for ease. Available in three Combrook tweeds; Lovat, Sage and Peat.', '39.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/compton_mens_country_baseball_cap_in_sage_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(854, 'COMGCA2', 'Combrook Collection > Compton Mens', 'Combrook Mens Extended Peak Country Tweed Flat Cap', 'Our new mens Combrook Extended Peak Tweed Flat Cap is perfect for keeping the rain from out of your eyes. Fully lined with a waterproof membrane to offer you complete protection form the elements. Available in a choice of country colours and will complement not only your other Alan Paine products, but a lot of your country clothing wardrobe.', '39.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_tweed_extended_flat_cap_combrook.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(855, 'COMGFIE', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Shooting Field Coat - Classic Fit', 'New Woodland Tweed ColourwayThis super field coat is a new addition to the popular Combrook tweed range. Engineered with a pure wool water repellent outer, this robust and hardwearing waterproof coat will keep you comfortable in the most testing of weather conditions.Unlike the Combrook Mens Waterproof Tweed Shooting Coat - Shooting Fit, this coat has a more tailored fit, with added features like an action back pleat to aid movement when shooting.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_mens_field_coat_in_sage.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(856, 'COMLCA1', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Caps & Hats', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Country Cap', 'We\'ve re-named our Compton Collection to the Combrook Collection. Don&amp;rsquo;t worry though, the products will be exactly the same and crafted to the high standard you&amp;rsquo;ve come to expect from Alan Paine.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_tweed_country_cap_combrook.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(857, 'COMLJAC', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Field Jacket - Shooting Fit', 'Three New Tweed Colourways - Juniper, Heather &amp;amp; GorseThis super stylish waterproof field jacket is the perfect choice for both town and country.With its pure wool, water repellent outer and designed to give you the perfect shooting fit, this jacket has all the functionality you&amp;rsquo;d expect from a shooting coat yet its elegant cut means it won&amp;rsquo;t look out of place worn on a trip into town. It has an array of useful pockets including two flap pockets, a secure map pocket under the front placket and a handy secure internal pocket.&amp;nbsp; The jacket also features a single back vent to aid movement and waterproof windbreaker cuffs to prevent any unwelcome gusts of wind rushing through the sleeves.&amp;nbsp;Available in a choice of stunning classic and contemporary tweed colourways this jacket is an absolute must.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_field_jacket_in_landscape_9_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(858, 'COMLPUS', 'Combrook Collection > Combrook Ladies', 'Combrook Ladies Small Tweed Purse', 'Combrook Ladies Small Tweed Purse comes with:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Tweed Outer&amp;bull; Leather Trim With Alan Paine Embossed Stud&amp;bull; 4 Credit Card Slots&amp;bull; 3 Slip In Pockets Suitable For Banknotes&amp;bull; 2 Further Receipt Compartments', '44.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/compton_ladies_small_tweed_purse_1_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(859, 'COMLPUL', 'Combrook Collection > Combrook Ladies', 'Combrook Ladies Large Tweed Purse', 'Combrook Ladies Large Tweed Purse comes with:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Tweed Outer&amp;bull; Leather Trim With Alan Paine Embossed Stud&amp;bull; 6 Credit Card Slots&amp;bull; 2 Slip In Pockets Suitable For Banknotes&amp;bull; 2 Further Receipt Compartments', '54.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_ladies_large_purse_in_avocado_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(860, 'COMLWRP', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Wrap', 'Ladies, look super stylish when the temperature dips with our stunning pure wool wrap.&amp;nbsp; With a handy water repellent outer the wrap comes in a choice of classic and contemporary tweed colourways and will look fantastic worn with one of our complementary tweed skirts, waterproof Cambridge breeks, jeans or, in fact, anything!&amp;nbsp; It comes with an attractive gilt leaf pin.', '119.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_country_wrap_in_avocado_gilt_leaf_pin_1_2.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(861, 'COMUCAP', 'Combrook Collection > Compton Mens', 'Combrook Unisex Tweed Country Cap', 'Combrook Unisex Tweed Country Cap comes with:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Wool Tweed Outer&amp;bull; Adjustable Leather Strap&amp;bull; Lined With A Polyester Lining&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Waterproof &amp;amp;amp; Breathable 5000mm / 5000 Mvp', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/u/n/unisex_tweed_shooting_flat_cap.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(862, 'RUTGSHW', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Rutland Mens Tweed Shooting Waistcoat - Shooting Fit', 'This shooting waistcoat is part of the long established Rutland tweed collection.&amp;nbsp; Crafted from durable wool blend tweed the waistcoat features a three button centre front fastening, two moleskin shoulder patches and two large cartridge pockets.&amp;nbsp;Designed to give you the perfect shooting fit the waistcoat also has two side vents to aid movement. &amp;nbsp;', '149.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_rutland_mens_shooting_waistcoat_in_lichen_1_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(863, 'RUTLWAX', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Rutland Ladies Wax & Tweed Jacket - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Shaped Feminine Fit With Wax Side Panels &amp;amp; Sleeves&amp;bull; Centre Front Zip Fastening With Studded Placket&amp;bull; Two Cartridge Pockets With Eyelet Drainage Holes&amp;bull; Two Handwarmer Pockets&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Single Back Vent To Aid Movement&amp;bull; Luxurious Quilted Lining&amp;bull; 60% Tweed Wool, 25&amp;pound; Acrylis, 10% Polyester &amp;amp; 5% Other', '199.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_shooting_tweed_wax_jacket_rutland.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(864, 'ACGGLV3', 'Mens > Gloves', 'Mens Knitted Back Gloves', 'Mens Knitted Back Gloves:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Sheepskin Leather Against The Palm With 100% Wool On Top Of The Hand&amp;bull; Top Fastening Strap With Branded Alan Paine Stud&amp;bull; Packaged In A Branded Alan Paine Gift Box', '54.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_knitted_back_gloves_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(865, 'ACGWGLV', 'Mens > Gloves', 'Mens Water Resistant Leather Shooting Gloves', 'Mens Water Resistant Leather Shooting Gloves:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Water Resistant Sheepskin Leather Lined With Ultra-fine Fleece&amp;bull; Left &amp;amp; Right-hand Trigger Finger Gloves With A Velcro Fold-back&amp;bull; Tweed Band With Alan Paine Embossed Studs&amp;bull; Stud Adjustable Strap&amp;bull; Pleated Elastic Under Palm For Greater Flexibility&amp;bull; Packaged In A Branded Alan Paine Gift Box', '54.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_water_resistant_leather_shotting_gloves_brown_peat.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(866, 'ACLGLV2', 'Womens > Gloves', 'Ladies Knitted Back Gloves', 'Ladies Knitted Back Gloves:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Sheepskin Leather Against The Palm With 100% Wool On Top Of The Hand&amp;bull; Top Fastening Strap With Branded Alan Paine Stud&amp;bull; Packaged In A Branded Alan Paine Gift Box', '54.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_knitted_back_gloves_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(867, 'ACLBGL2', 'Womens > Bags, Luggage & Purses', 'Ladies Leather Handbag', 'Our Alan Paine luxurious leather handbag is a must-have that\'s designed with style and function. Made from the finest oak leather, with a striking check lining, the spacious interior of this superior quality handbag will easily accommodate all of your everyday essentials.An interior zip compartment offers organisation for your keys, purse and phone on the go, all secured with a flap-over and magnetic stud fastening.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Base&amp;nbsp; : Width 30cm | Length 8.5cm&amp;bull; Height: 24cm&amp;bull; Trimmed With A High Quality Hardwearing Oak Leather&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Lined With A Luxurious Check Lining&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Secure Internal Zipped Pocket&amp;bull; Buckle Fastened Flap Closure&amp;nbsp;', '174.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_ladies_handbag_in_oak_leather.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(868, 'ACLBGT2', 'Womens > Bags, Luggage & Purses', 'Ladies Tweed Handbag', 'Ladies Tweed Handbag&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Base&amp;nbsp; : Width 30cm | Length 8.5cm&amp;bull; Height: 24cm&amp;bull; Outer Fabric 100% Wool Tweed&amp;bull; Trimmed With A High Quality Hardwearing Oak Leather&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Lined With A Luxurious Check Lining&amp;bull; Buckle Fastened Flap Closure&amp;nbsp;', '144.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_ladies_handbag_in_landscape_tweed_with_oak_brown_leather_handle_trim_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(869, 'ACUBGC7', 'Mens > Bags & Luggage', 'Mens Canvas Wash Bag', 'Mens Canvas Wash Bag&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; False Buckles With Stud Fastening&amp;bull; Folding Out To A Multi Pocket Wash Bag&amp;bull; Antique Brass Buckle Fittings&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Antique Brass Hook On The Inside To Hang The Bag Open&amp;nbsp;', '69.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_men_s_canvas_wash_bag_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(870, 'ACUBGL6', 'Mens > Bags & Luggage', 'Mens Leather Wash Bag', 'The Alan Paine classic men\'s leather wash bag is the must-have accessory for every gentleman whilst travelling.Made from the finest oak leather with a striking check lining, the spacious interior of this superior quality toiletry bag will easily accommodate all of your shaving and toiletry essentials.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Base&amp;nbsp; : Width 11cm | Length 25cm&amp;bull; Height: 15cm&amp;bull; Double Zip Entry&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Internal Zipped Pocket&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Handy Carry Loop On Zips&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Lined With An Attractive Check Lining&amp;nbsp;', '69.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_men_s_leather_wash_bag.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(871, 'DOGCT1', 'Chistmas > Christmas Gifts For Pets', 'Tweed Dog Coat', 'Introducing the new Alan Paine Tweed Dog Coat to our Autumn Winter collection. Keep your best friend warm, dry and stylish whilst out and about.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Fleece Lined&amp;bull; Velcro Adjustable Body Strap&amp;bull; Front Velcro Fastening&amp;bull; Nylon Showerproof Outer With Tweed Panels&amp;nbsp;Size GuideXS - Back Length 30cm S - &amp;nbsp; Back Length 40cm M - &amp;nbsp;Back Length 50cm L - &amp;nbsp; Back Length 60cm XL- &amp;nbsp;Back Length 70cm', '49.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/b/b/bb_in_the_alan_paine_tweed_dog_coat.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(872, 'RICUOTR', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Richmond Mens Overtrouser', 'Made from 100% waxed cotton outer the men’s Alan Paine Richmond over trousers will offer durability against brambles and animal work whilst keeping you protected from the weather. Side slits allow easy access to your pockets on your base trousers so you can easily reach your phone or wallet.', '59.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/r/i/ricuotr.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(873, 'SOCG01', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Mens Country Socks', 'Mens Country Socks&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Reinforced Toe&amp;bull; 85% Wool | 10% Nylon | 5% Lycra&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)', '29.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_mens_sock_in_bordeaux_olive_3.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(874, 'SOCL51', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Skirts & Trousers', 'Ladies Country Socks', 'Ladies Country Socks&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Reinforced Toe&amp;bull; 85% Wool | 10% Nylon | 5% Lycra&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)', '29.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_ladies_socks_in_seagreen_pink.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(875, 'APM071', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Ties', 'Mens Knitted Wool Country Tie', 'It&amp;rsquo;s the finishing touches that matter &amp;ndash; and the classic Alan Paine Knitted Wool tie is the perfect addition to any country wardrobe.Wear it out in the field or even to the pub on a Sunday afternoon &amp;ndash; in a choice of five colours this tie is sure to complement almost everything in your countrywear repertoire.Plus, the lovely Alan Paine branded presentation box means that this country tie would make an excellent gift for the sporting man.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;100% Wool Outer&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Packaged In A Leather-Look Gift Box&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Tie Length 150cm', '39.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/men_s_knitted_wool_country_ties_4.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(876, 'APM072', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Ties', 'Mens Knitted Patterned Wool Country Tie', 'It&amp;rsquo;s the finishing touches that matter &amp;ndash; and the classic Alan Paine Patterned Wool tie is the perfect addition to any country wardrobe.Wear it out in the field or even to the pub on a Sunday afternoon &amp;ndash; in a choice of two patterned colours this tie is sure to complement almost everything in your countrywear repertoire.Plus, the lovely Alan Paine branded presentation box means that this country tie would make an excellent gift for the sporting man.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;100% Wool Outer&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Packaged In A Leather-Look Gift Box&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Tie Length 150cm', '44.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_knitted_patterned_wool_country_tie_sk9.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(877, 'FALUTRG', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Falmouth Tregging - Regular Fit', 'Falmouth Tregging:&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Regular Fit&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Water Repellent Waxed Cotton Outter&amp;bull; Side Slits For Trouser Access&amp;bull; Buckle Adjustable Hem&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Fully Lined With Polyester&amp;bull; 32 Inside Leg', '59.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/f/a/falutrg.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(878, 'B79U37', 'English Explorer', 'Mens English Explorer Donegal Merino Wool Crew Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', 'Last years best-selling English Explorer sweater is back again for Autumn Winter 2017. Chunky in look, soft and pleasing to wear and will look great by the fireside of your local pub. These delightfully donegal jumpers are knitted in warm autumnal colours flecked with a multitude of complementary tones.', '110.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_donegal_merino_wool_jumper_crew_neck.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(879, 'B50U29', '', 'Mens Lambswool Cable Crew Neck Mens Jumper - Updated Fit', 'Layer up in style this season with the Men&amp;rsquo;s Lambswool Cable Crew Neck jumper, crafted from 100% lambswool for an added touch of luxury and warmth. This stylish crew neck sweater features a cable knit detailing, giving you a classic look you are sure to love!', '104.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/1/_/1_b50u29_mrb.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(880, '149D28', 'English Explorer', 'Mens English Explorer Shenstone Wool Blend Vee Neck Jumper with Windblock Lining - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;NEW COLOURS FOR AUTUMN WINTER 2017&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;This vee-neck jumper has been especially designed to offer you superior protection against extreme cold and windy weather conditions.&amp;nbsp;Fully lined with 100% Windblock breathable fabric&amp;nbsp;with added stretch, making it ideal for the great outdoors.&amp;bull; 80% Wool | 20% Polyamide&amp;bull; Windblock Lining&amp;bull; Vee Neck&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Updated Fit - Our most regular &amp;amp; modern fit&amp;nbsp;(see Size Guide below for more details and Euro/US conversion).&amp;nbsp;', '88.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/e/x/explorer_shenstone_wool_blend_vee_neck_mens_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51');
