(881, '149D29', 'English Explorer', 'Mens English Explorer Wilshaw Wool Blend 1/2 Zip Mock Neck with Windblock Lining - Updated Fit', 'Our men\'s English Explorer Wilshaw 1/2 Zip Sweater will become&amp;nbsp;a staple part of your wardrobe if you live and enjoy outdoors sports.&amp;nbsp;This lightweight Half Zip sweater has a country and sporting look and the fully windblocking breathable lining adds additional protection from those harsh wintery winds.Our model wears a UK 42 &amp;nbsp;/ EU 50 / US M &amp;nbsp;and is 185 cm / 6\'1&amp;rdquo; tall. For more information on sizing please click on the &amp;lsquo;SIZE GUIDE&amp;rsquo; link below.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 80% Wool | 20% Polyamide&amp;bull; Windblock Lining&amp;bull; Half Zip With Mock Neck&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Updated Fit - Our most regular &amp;amp; modern fit&amp;nbsp;(see Size Guide below for more details and Euro/US conversion).&amp;nbsp;', '104.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/e/x/explorer_wilshaw_wool_blend_half_zip_mock_neck_mens_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(882, 'AYLGWND', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Aylsham Mens Fleece Windblock - Classic Fit', 'Be prepared for any weather this season with the men&amp;rsquo;s Alan Paine Alysham Windblock Fleece, this waterproof and breathable fleece means you can enjoy the outdoors no matter what the weather brings. Tailored to a classic fit for added comfort and wearability, as well as back waist adjusters so this fleece as be adjusted for a fit to suit you. The elasticated cuff helps keep the colder and wet weather out, finishing this fleece with contrasting colour piping and outside collar for added style and attention to detail.', '129.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_fleece_windblock_aylsham.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(883, 'ACUBGT4', 'Womens > Bags, Luggage & Purses', 'Tweed Laptop Bag - Landscape', 'This Alan Paine Tweed Laptop Bag is perfect for carrying all your electronic devices and everyday essentials.&amp;nbsp;It also features luxurious leather carry handles, a removable shoulder strap and trimmed with hard wearing leather with a striking check lining so you can be comfortable and stylish in your day to day.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Base&amp;nbsp; : Width 10cm | Length 41cm&amp;bull; Height: 29cm&amp;bull; Outer Fabric 100% Pure Wool Tweed&amp;bull; Lined With A Luxurious Check Lining&amp;bull; Trimmed With A High Quality Hardwearing Leather&amp;bull; Embossed Alan Paine Leather Badge At Front Of Bag&amp;bull; Secure Zip Closure&amp;bull; Internal Padded Laptop Pocket With Velcro Secure Strap (38cm*20cm)&amp;bull; Internal Zip Secured Pocket&amp;bull; Internal Leather Pen Holding Loops &amp;amp; Pocket&amp;bull; Luxurious Leather Carry Handle&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Including Calico Dust Bag&amp;bull; Detachable &amp;amp; Adjustable Cotton Webbing Shoulder Strap (full length 100cm)&amp;nbsp;', '209.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/t/w/tweed_laptop_bag_landscape.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(884, '632224', 'Mens > Cashmere Scarves', 'Westerdale Cashmere Mini Square Check Scarf', 'This luxury scarf from Alan Paine is great for wrapping up against the cold in style. A large square check scarf crafted from pure cashmere.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 100% Cashmere&amp;bull; Length 180cm&amp;bull; Width 30cm&amp;bull; Rectangular&amp;bull; Fringing At Both Ends&amp;bull; Hand Wash Only', '97.50 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cashmere_mini_square_checked_scarf.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(885, 'COMLMIDX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Mid Length Classic Fit - Clearance Colour', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! Compton Ladies Tweed Mid Length Coat is a pure wool tweed 3-buttoned mid-length coat featuring two flap pockets, a ticket pocket, single back vent and lined with a stunning contrast lining.Our luxurious soft handle Compton Tweeds are tightly woven for us using a natural array of twisted coloured yarns to create modern yet classic colourways.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_mid-length_coat_in_meadow_4_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(886, 'COMLCOTX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Coat Shooting Fit - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! This waterproof coat has been one of our most popular jackets since the inception of the Combrook collection. Our pure wool Combrook tweed is specially woven for us and not only is it a durable and functional tweed it also boasts an extremely soft handle. We pride ourselves on sourcing beautiful fabrics with eye-catching colourful overchecks.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_shooting_coat_in_meadow_3_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(887, 'COMLS49X', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Long Skirt 49cm - Clearance Colours', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;This popular skirt is from our Combrook ladies collection. Crafted from a pure wool tweed with a water repellent outer there&amp;rsquo;s no need to worry if you get caught in an unexpected shower.Available in a choice of country colours the skirt is fully lined with a striking contrast lining and there&amp;rsquo;s a cleverly concealed side zip.', '119.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_skirt_in_meadow_4_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(888, 'COMLS42X', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Pleated Hem Skirt 42cm - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! This popular skirt is from our Combrook ladies collection. Crafted from a pure wool tweed with a water repellent outer there&amp;rsquo;s no need to worry if you get caught in an unexpected shower.Available in a choice of country colours the skirt is fully lined with a striking contrast lining and there&amp;rsquo;s a cleverly concealed side zip.', '114.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_compton_ladies_tweed_country_skirt_in_dusk_42cm_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(889, 'AYLLWCTX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Aylsham Ladies Fleece Waistcoat Classic Fit - Clearance Colours', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Our popular Aylsham ladies fleece waistcoat is a useful addition to any wardrobe. Perfect for warmer days worn over a shirt or ideal as an extra layer underneath a coat.The waistcoat has a robust front zipper and has two handy zipped pockets. The waist can be adjusted to ensure a snug, stylish comfortable fit. Contrast piping around the armholes, on the collar and either side of the zip is a stylish addition.', '79.99 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/y/aylsham_country_ladies_fleece_waistcoat_in_brown_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(890, 'COMGBLRX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Blazers', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Blazer Classic Fit - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! If the occasion calls for something smart then our Combrook Mens Blazer with its 100% Wool water repellent tweed outer certainly ‘fits the bill’.Available in a selection of country colours, this exquisite garment will certainly be a valued addition to any wardrobe.Superbly tailored with a 3 button front closure, double back vents, ticket pocket, two internal pockets along with its contrast lining tonal with the tweed over check to complete the look.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_mens_tweed_blazer_in_forest_green_5_1_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(891, 'COMGBRKX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Breeks', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Breeks - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! Our pure wool Combrook tweed breeks will prove to be an invaluable addition to your shooting wardrobe and have consistently been one of our most popular items.Not only functional and durable they look super smart too! Crafted from pure wool tweed these breeks come complete with a water repellent outer so no nasty surprises if caught in a shower whilst out in the field.The breeks have two handy side pockets, two button secured back pockets and, to ensure a really comfortable wear, are fully lined with cotton. What&amp;rsquo;s more they also have Velcro-adjustable hems.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_mens_tweed_shooting_breeks_in_forest_green.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(892, 'COMGCA2X', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Mens Extended Peak Country Tweed Flat Cap - Clearance Colour', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! Our Combrook pure wool tweed mens flat cap is waterproof and breathable; an absolute must when you&amp;rsquo;re out in the field. It&amp;rsquo;s available in a choice of country colours and will complement not only your other Alan Paine products, but a lot of your country clothing wardrobe.With its classic peak front and luxurious lining the Compton Mens Flat Cap will keep you warm and your head dry when it counts.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Waterproof &amp;amp; Breathable 5000 mm / 5000 Mvp&amp;bull; Fully Lined&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Extended Peak&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/compton_mens_tweed_extended_peak_country_flat_cap_in_forest_green_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(893, 'COMGCOTX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Coats & Jackets', 'Combrook Mens Waterproof Shooting Tweed Coat  - Shooting Fit - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! The Combrook Mens Shooting Coat has been part of our product offering since the launch of the country collection and continues to be one of the most popular garments in the Combrook range.Engineered with a 100% wool water repellent outer, this robust and hardwearing garment is armed with a waterproof &amp;amp; breathable membrane to keep you comfortable in the most testing of weather conditions. Insulated with a soft polyester wadding alongside deep manly hand warmer pockets and storm cuffs, all to keep you warm on those cold wintery mornings.Featuring two large cartridge pockets with drainage holes along with flap retainer straps hidden inside the top pockets definitely will prove useful on those shoot days. Housing a map pocket under the front storm placket and with two further secure internal pockets the Combrook Coat certainly fits the bill for a impeccable shooting coat.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_mens_shooting_coat_in_forest_green_12.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(894, 'COMGFIEX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Field Coat Classic Fit - Clearance Colour', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! This super field coat is a new addition to the popular Combrook tweed range.&amp;nbsp; Engineered with a pure wool water repellent outer, this robust and hardwearing waterproof coat will keep you comfortable in the most testing of weather conditions. The jacket has waterproof windbreaker cuffs to keep the cuff area snug against the body and prevent gusts of wind rushing through the sleeve, plus a waterproof drip strip at the bottom of the lining.&amp;nbsp;Featuring two large cartridge pockets with drainage holes, deep manly hand-warmer pockets and a handy secure internal pocket this new field coat certainly fits the bill.&amp;nbsp; It is available in a choice of classic and contemporary tweed colourways.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_crombrook_mens_field_coat_in_forest_green_13.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(895, 'COMGWCTX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Shooting Waistcoat Shooting Fit - Clearance Colour', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! Specially designed for shooting, this fabulous waistcoat looks great over an Alan Paine jumper. With its classic shooting silhouette this product allows you to take unhindered movement when it matters.Crafted from a water repellent pure wool tweed the waistcoat features a 3 button centre front fastening, an internal pocket and useful side slits to aid movement when shooting.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_mens_tweed_shooting_vest_in_forest_green_3_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(896, '016Y40', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Hingston Cotton Textured Washed Out Effect Shawl Collar - Updated Fit', 'Our cotton texture washed out effect knitwear with shawl collar, in 100% cotton, is an absolute must-have for this season. A unique,&amp;nbsp;3-dimensional structured texture gives this piece of knitwear a distinctive look. Complete with a cosy shawl collar this knit&amp;nbsp;looks just as smart paired with jeans and trainers as it does with trousers and shoes.&amp;bull; Updated Fit&amp;bull; 100% Cotton&amp;bull; 7g&amp;bull; Collar Style: Shawl Neck&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)&amp;nbsp;', '110.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/h/i/hingston_cotton_textured_washed_out_effect_shawl_collar_landscape.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(897, '189C19', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Pentlow Lightweight Cotton Silk Cashmere Long Sleeve Polo Shirt - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Upgrade your knitwear this season with this lightweight long-sleeved polo shirt is crafted from a blend of soft pima cotton, silk and cashmere.&amp;nbsp;The unfussy look and clean styling of this long-sleeve polo shirt ensures it will pair effortlessly with your separates.', '91.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cotton_cashmere_long_sleeve_polo_shirt_carolina_blue_1_7.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(898, '196T20', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Leysmill Cotton Cashmere Vee Crew Jumper - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;This cotton cashmere crew neck is a timeless wardrobe essential which can be worn with a pair of jeans or chinos.Crafted from a luxurious blend of pima cotton and cashmere this plain knit vee neck is a updated fit, rather than a traditional classic fit.All Alan Paine knitwear is fully fashioned; each garment is knitted to shape on the knitting machine and not cut and sewn.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced &amp;ndash; and the mitre of the &amp;ldquo;Crew&amp;rdquo; neck is closed by hand to give a perfect finish.&amp;nbsp;', '81.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cotton_cashmere_crew_neck_sweater_dark_navy_1_7.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(899, 'LS1703', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Polo Shirts', 'Marlow Stretch Pique Polo Shirt With Shoulder Stitch Detail - Updated Fit', 'This limited edition men\'s stretch pique polo shirt is an absolute must if you want to stand out from the crowd this summer.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Updated Fit&amp;bull; 97% Cotton | 3% Elastic&amp;bull; Three Button Fastening&amp;bull; Polo Collar&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Short Sleeve &amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion).', '49.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/a/marlow_stretch_pique_polo_shirt_with_shoulder_stitch_detail_white.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(900, 'COMGCAPX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Flat Cap - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! Our Combrook pure wool tweed mens flat cap is waterproof and breathable; an absolute must when you&amp;rsquo;re out in the field. It&amp;rsquo;s available in a choice of country colours and will complement not only your other Alan Paine products, but a lot of your country clothing wardrobe.With its classic peak front and luxurious lining the Combrook Mens Flat Cap will keep you warm and your head dry when it counts.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Waterproof &amp;amp; Breathable 5000 mm / 5000 Mvp&amp;bull; Fully Lined', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/compton_mens_tweed_country_flat_cap_in_forest_green_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(901, '196C12', 'New Arrivals > Knitwear', 'Selhurst Cotton Cashmere Half Zip Mock Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Warm and comfortable, our best-selling men&amp;rsquo;s half zip sweater is incredibly will become you go-to layering piece of knitwear this season. Features a stunning half zip stand up collar, long sleeves with ribbed cuffs and a beautiful lightweight Cotton Cashmere composition.', '91.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_cotton_cashmere_half_zip_pullover_atlanta_1_1_7.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(902, '196F05', '', 'Hampton Cotton Cashmere Textured Crew Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Crafted from a luxurious blend of Pima cotton and cashmere this plain knit crew neck is a updated fit, rather than a traditional classic fit. A unique, 3-dimensional structured texture gives this piece of knitwear a distinctive look.All Alan Paine knitwear is fully fashioned; each garment is knitted to shape on the knitting machine and not cut and sewn.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Updated Fit&amp;bull; 92% Cotton | 8% Cashmere&amp;bull; 12g&amp;bull; Collar Style: Crew Neck&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)', '105.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/h/a/hampton_cotton_cashmere_textured_crew_neck_jumper_sand.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(903, '189F01', 'Mens > Knitwear > Slipovers', 'Cransford Lightweight Cotton Silk Cashmere Half Zip Mock Vest - Updated Fit', 'Our new lightweight&amp;nbsp;blend of soft pima cotton, silk and cashmere knits is our signature piece of our Spring Summer 2018 collection. This half zip mock neck vest is&amp;nbsp;an essential layering tool for your smart cool waether wardrobe.&amp;nbsp;Easy to dress up or down, it looks just as smart paired with jeans and trainers as it does with trousers and shoes.', '90.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/r/cransford_lightweight_cotton_silk_cashmere_half_zip_mock_vest_rose.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(904, '196A43', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cotton Cashmere Crew Neck Jumper - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;Crafted from a luxurious natural blend of Pima Cotton and Cashmere for day-long comfort. This plain knit crew neck i&amp;nbsp;is a versatile wardrobe staple, essential for work and play and will become your favourite wardrobe essential.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Perfect for pepping up your everyday wear or even as the centrepiece of an evening outfit, this stunning sweater is guaranteed to see you through the Spring / Summer season and beyond.', '70.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/h/a/hannah_cotton_cashmere_crew_neck_jumper_orchid.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(905, '196A44', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cotton Cashmere Vee Neck Jumper - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;SUMMER SALE - HURRY! LIMTED STOCK&amp;nbsp;Crafted from a luxurious natural blend of Pima Cotton and Cashmere for day-long comfort. This plain knit vee neck i&amp;nbsp;is a versatile wardrobe staple, essential for work and play and will become your favourite wardrobe essential.&amp;nbsp;Perfect for pepping up your everyday wear or even as the centrepiece of an evening outfit, this stunning sweater is guaranteed to see you through the Spring / Summer season and beyond.', '70.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/1/9/196a44steelblue.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(906, '196Y28', '', 'Peckleton Cotton Cashmere Argyle Front Vee Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Crafted from a luxurious blend of Pima cotton and cashmere this plain knit crew neck is a updated fit, rather than a traditional classic fit. A unique, 3-dimensional structured texture gives this piece of knitwear a distinctive look.All Alan Paine knitwear is fully fashioned; each garment is knitted to shape on the knitting machine and not cut and sewn.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced.', '90.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/p/e/peckleton_cotton_cashmere_argyle_front_vee_neck_jumper_seb_atl_blu_gym.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(907, 'LODGGIL', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Loden Mens Gilet - Classic Fit', 'New for Autumn Winter 2017 comes this stylish Loden Men\'s Gilet perfect for layering up in style on those casual days this season and beyond, crafted from 100% loden wool to offer you a stylish yet durable design you are sure to love!&amp;nbsp;Designed with technical excellence, it has a soft &amp;nbsp;mock suede collar &amp;amp; quilted outer collar for additional warmth and comfort. Complete with a two-way front zipper and studded placket for complete protection so this quilted loden gilet not only looks good, it has been designed to withstand our unpredictable winter weather due to the water repellent outer that will keep you protected when enjoying the great outdoors.', '179.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_loden_mens_gilet_12.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(908, 'LODGQUJ', 'Mens > Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Loden Mens Quilted Jacket - Classic Fit', 'Our new Autumn Winter 2017 Loden Mens Quilted Jacket is made from 100% Loden Wool which will keep you exceptionally warm and looking relaxed and stylish with its tailored, smart fit.&amp;nbsp;Designed with technical excellence, it has a soft &amp;nbsp;mock suede collar &amp;amp; quilted outer collar for additional warmth and comfort.Complete with a waterproof &amp;amp; breathable membrane, a two-way front zipper and studded placket for complete protection so this quilted loden jacket not only looks good, it has been designed to withstand our unpredictable winter weather due to the water repellent outer that will keep you protected when enjoying the great outdoors.', '264.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_loden_mens_quilted_jacket_11.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(909, 'BERGBRK', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Berwick Mens Waterproof Breeks', 'New this seasonn comes our men\'s waterproof shooting breeks from our award nominated Berwick Waterproof Collection. These&amp;nbsp;versatile breeks feature a buckle adjustable hem, 2 zip secure back pockets to protect your valuables &amp;amp; 2 hand side pockets.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_mens_waterproof_breeks_in_olive.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(910, 'BERGSHW', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Berwick Mens Waterproof Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'New to our Autumn Winter 2017 collection comes this smart, functional men\'s waterproof shooting vest. This practical waistcoat has all the features you need for a successful day out&amp;nbsp;offering you great freedom of movement. Waterproof and breathable making it easy to enjoy all that county life has to offer.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_mens_waterproof_shooting_waistcoat.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(911, 'BERGTRO', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Berwick Mens Waterproof Trousers - Regular Fit', 'Following on from the success of our Berwick Waterproof Coat&amp;nbsp;we\'ve introduced these new technical waterproof trousers for Autumn Winter 2017. These&amp;nbsp;waterproof trousers feature a high elastic back along with a side gusset at the hem and a zipped fly at the front, the secure zipped pockets with overlay flaps help to protect valuables.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_mens_overtrousers_in_olive.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(912, 'KENGCOT', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Kexby Mens Performance Coat - Classic Fit', 'Two New Colours - Olive &amp;amp; NavyFrom our new Kexby collection comes this techical men\'s performance coat. A multi functional coat which can be used for all outdoor sporting activities where full windproof, waterproof and breathability are essential. Specifically designed with the game shooter in mind with and action back and studded back vents to aid movement.Fully waterproof and breathable with all the pockets one could possibly need. It features two way centre zip with studded placket, top collar trimmed with alcantara and waterproof windbreaker cuffs make this the perfect shooting jacket available in a full range of sizes.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_kexby_mens_performance_coat_in_olive_1_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(913, 'KENGGIL', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Kexby Mens Gilet - Classic Fit', 'Two New Colours - Olive &amp;amp; NavyComplete your layered look with our new men&amp;rsquo;s Kexby Quilted Gilet, ideal for teaming with jeans and worn over your favourite Alan Paine jumper for a stylish yet casual country look.This stylish men\'s quilted gilet features a durable water repellent cotton outer, a two-way centre front zip, two zip-secured hand-warmer pockets and two secure internal pockets for all your valuables.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_kexby_mens_gilet_in_olive_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(914, 'KENGSHW', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Kexby Mens Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'This techical men\'s shooting waistcoat is the perfect shooting vest with all the essential features to equip you for the new shooting season ahead.&amp;nbsp;Complete with water repellent outer to protect you from sudden down pours,&amp;nbsp;4 front centre fastening buttons for a streamline fit that can be worn alone or under your shooting coat and&amp;nbsp;two large cartridge pockets with plenty of room for your essential equipment.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_kexby_mens_shooting_waistcoat_in_olive_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(915, 'KENGSMK', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Kexby Mens Waterproof Smock - Shooting Fit', 'New Colour For AW18 - OliveThis techical men\'s stalking smock is multi functional and can be used for all outdoor sporting activities where full windproof, waterproof and breathability are essential. Primarily designed for stalking, it features a quarter zip front opening with double stud fastening storm flap, double pouch pocket with seperate compartments, a zip-secured hand warming pocket behind the pouch pocket for your valuables, detachable fleece lined hood, quilted lining and adjustable sleeve tabs and storm cuffs.It is also equipped with a waterproof side seam zip to aid removing the garment.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_kexby_mens_waterproof_smock_in_olive_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(916, 'AYLGSHW', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Aylsham Mens Fleece Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'New for Autumn Winter 2017 is our Aylsham Fleece Shooting Waistcoat. It is perfect for early to mid-season shooting when you don\'t always require the bulk of a shooting coat, but still need to stay warm. It features large front cartridge pockets and mock suede shoulder patches and can be adjusted at the waist for a snug fit.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/y/aylsham_mens_shooting_fleece_waistcoat_in_russet_3.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(917, 'BUXUFLC ', 'Mens > Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Buxton Unisex Fleece - Classic Fit', 'The Alan Paine Buxton fleece is a unisex fleece pullover which features a luxurious handle looped fleece outer. The stylish cotton trims and elasticated cuffs and hem make this a really comfortable fleece to wear for everyday use, or as a layering piece in the shooting field.', '69.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/b/u/buxton_unisex_fleecein_dark_navy.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(918, '050D83', 'Mens > Knitwear > Jumpers > Lambswool Jumpers', 'Burford Men\'s Lambswool Vee Neck Pullover - Classic Fit', 'The Burford Men\'s Lambswool V Neck Jumper makes for a versatile layering piece as the cold weather sets in, giving you the perfect option to leave the house without a jacket if it\'s not quite cold enough.', '79.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_lambswool_pullover_burford.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(919, 'AYLLSWC', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Aylsham Ladies Fleece Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'Due to the success of our Aylsham ladies fleece gilets we\'ve introduced a limited amount of shooting fleece waistcoats to our new Autumn Winter 2017 collection. Perfect for warmer days worn over a shirt or ideal as an extra layer of warmth underneath a coat.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_aylsham_ladies_shooting_waistcoat_in_dark_navy_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(920, 'BERLJAC', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Berwick Ladies Waterproof Jacket - Classic Fit', 'Following on from our succesful launch of the Berwick Ladies Waterproof Shooting Coat comes this stylish waterproof jacket with detachable hood with detachable mock fur trim. Designed to keep you dry and warm this jacket is both waterproof and breathable with a fleece lining garuanteed to keep that wind at bay.&amp;nbsp;This stylish jacket offers you a feminine design, finished with a belted waist to give you a flattering and feminine look. Packed full of features&amp;nbsp;including a map pocket, 2 hand warming packets and zip-secured internal pockets to keep your valuables safe.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_ladies_waterproof_jacket_inolive.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(921, 'BERLLON', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Berwick Ladies Waterproof Long Coat - Classic Fit', 'Stay dry in style this season and beyond with our new Berwick Ladies Waterproof Long Coat, part of our award-nominated Berwick Waterproofs Collection.&amp;nbsp; With its feminine cut this must-have coat has a waterproof and breathable cotton blend outer, a detachable hood with detachable mock fur trim and a large back vent to aid movement.&amp;nbsp; It has a useful map pocket, cosy hand-warmer pockets, lower lining leg straps to secure the coat (ideal on a windy day) and stud adjustable sleeve tabs.&amp;nbsp; What&amp;rsquo;s more, it comes with a luxurious striking patterned lining.This long length coat will keep you warm and dry when those unpredictable downpours arrive.&amp;nbsp; It usefully features&amp;nbsp;an interactive zip to accommodate the&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Alan Paine Aylsham Fleece Waistcoat&amp;nbsp;should you need an extra layer for bitterly cold days.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_ladies_waterproof_long_coat_in_dark_navy_1_.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(922, 'COMLSHW', 'Combrook Collection > Combrook Ladies', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Shooting Waistcoat - Classic Fit', 'Three New Tweed Colourways - Juniper, Heather &amp;amp; GorseNew to our ladies Combrook range comes this classically designed technical ladies shooting waistcoat made from 100% pure wool tweed with a water repellent finish. This beautiful waistcoat features&amp;nbsp;with faux suede shoulder panels to aid gun mount and roomy cartridge pockets finished with a contrasting lining to compliment the tweed.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_ladies_shooting_waistcoat_in_juniper_11.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(923, 'SURGBLR ', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Surrey Mens Tweed Sports Jacket - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Our classically styled Surrey Men&amp;rsquo;s Tweed Sports Jacket is traditional 100% wool jacket that will look fantastic layered over your favourite shirt and tie this season. This beautifully crafted jacket is perfect for any country gent, featuring double back vents to give you added comfort and movement when you need it most. This jacket boasts 100% woollen outer for an added touch of warmth and luxury, finished with a contrast lining to match over &amp;ndash; check.', '274.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_country_sports_jacket_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(924, 'SURGBRK ', '', 'Surrey Mens Tweed Breeks - Regular Fit', 'Our Surrey Men&amp;rsquo;s Tweed Breeks are finely tailored pure wool tweed breeks, fully lined with cotton for comfort and featuring two front side and two button-secured back pockets with Velcro&amp;reg; adjustable leg hem.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_tweed_shooting_breeks_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(925, 'SURGCOT ', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Surrey Mens Tweed Waterproof Shooting Coat - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;The Surrey Men&amp;rsquo;s Tweed Shooting Coat is made to the highest specifications so you can be sure you are completely prepared for the rigours of British country pursuits. It has all of the key features you would expect from a great shooting coat. The coat is both waterproof, breathable and equipped with windbreaker cuffs; it also offers excellent freedom of movement and has a Alcantara&amp;reg; collar for comfort.', '349.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_waterproof_shooting_coat_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(926, 'SURGWCT', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Surrey Mens Tweed Shooting Vest - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Our Surrey Men&amp;rsquo;s Shooting Vest is a very smart, tailored men\'s shooting vest with reinforced Alcantara shoulder patches and large cartridge pockets for keeping your essentials within easy reach. This men\'s waistcoat has an adjustable back belt to give you a great streamline fit to avoid snagging when active.', '224.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_shooting_vest_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(927, 'SURLBLA', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Surrey Ladies Tweed Blazer - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;A must-have for every country wardrobe. Our Surrey Ladies Tweed Blazer has been crafted from 100% wool for a comfortable, warm feel that is perfect for both formal and countryside wear.', '279.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/s/u/surrey_ladies_tweed_hacking_jacket_orchard_3.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(928, 'SURLHA1 ', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Caps & Hats', 'Surrey Ladies Tweed Country Hat', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Perfect for complementing your country attire; the Surrey Ladies Tweed Hat comes with an 100% tweed wool outer with wax cotton bow &amp;amp; trim edge, perfect for when town meets country.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 100% Wool Outer&amp;bull; Waxed Cotton Bow Trim &amp;amp; Rim Edge&amp;bull; Polyester Satin Lining&amp;nbsp;', '54.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/s/u/surrey_ladies_tweed_hat_in_orchard.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(929, 'SURLHJA', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Surrey Ladies Tweed Hacking Jacket - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;The Surrey Ladies Tweed Hacking Jacket is a stylish show jacket with a flattering, comfortable fit, with two rear vents to aid movement and three button closure. Available in two beautifil tweed colourays, Orchard &amp;amp; Hazel, with stuning attractive lining.&amp;nbsp;', '2905.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_tweed_country_hacking_jacket_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(930, 'SURLMTC ', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Jackets & Coats', 'Surrey Ladies Tweed Mid-Thigh Coat - Classic Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Our Surrey Ladies Tweed Mid-Thigh Coat&amp;nbsp;is a pure wool tweed 3-buttoned mid-length coat featuring two contrasted jetted pockets, single back vent and lined with a stunning contrast lining.', '415.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_tweed_country_knee_length_coat_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(931, 'SURLLSK', 'Womens > Skirts & Trousers', 'Surrey Ladies Long Tweed Skirt - 72cm Length', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;Completing our new Surrey range is this stylish long skirt. Team with either the mid-thigh overcoat or hacking jacket for a sophisticated look, perfect for a day at the races or out in the field. The mid-calf length design with straight cut finish offers you a relaxed yet feminine design.&amp;nbsp;Crafted from 100% tweed wool, finished with a water repellent coating, contrast lining and complete with invisible zip entry.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; Water Repellent Outer&amp;bull; Luxurious Raccon Fur Detachable Collar Trim&amp;bull; Button Fastening&amp;bull; Soft Mock Suede Inner Collar For Comfort&amp;bull; Fully Lined With A Striking Attractive Lining&amp;bull; Twh Hand-Warmer Pockets&amp;bull; Side Seams Split For Sleeves&amp;bull; 81cm Length&amp;bull; 100% Wool&amp;bull;&amp;nbsp;Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)&amp;nbsp;', '109.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/a/ladies_long_tweed_country_skirt_surrey.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(932, '128G17', '', 'Mens Merino Wool Basketweave Crew Neck Jumper - Trim Fit', 'A textured basketweave stitch on this new AW17 crew neck jumper takes a basic pullover to another level. Made from 100% Merino Wool giving it a&amp;nbsp;softer, finer and breathable feel to the jumper.Please not this garment is part of our Trim Fit range, our most contemporary fit. Trim Fit styles are very closely cut across the full body, thus creating a figure-hugging shape with a streamlined silhouette.&amp;nbsp;', '130.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_merino_wool_basketweave_crew_neck_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(933, '139G32', 'Geelong Wool Jumpers', 'Mens Geelong Wool Argyle Vee Neck Jumper - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;Our Biggest Ever Winter Sale&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Hurry, Limited Colours &amp;amp; Sizes!&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;This beautifully crafted jumper made from pure geelong lambswool will be a great addition to your wardrobe. Details include timeless and simple diamond knit&amp;nbsp;argyle pattern to the front, a v-neck and our most regular updated fit.The beauty of Geelong wool is that, despite the lightness, it gives a unique combination of warmth, softness and drape.&amp;nbsp;The argyle style was taken up and popularised by golf aficionados such as the Duke of Windsor in the 1920s.&amp;nbsp;Our model is 6&amp;rsquo;2&amp;rdquo; and wears a UK size 42&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 100% Geelong Wool&amp;bull; Argyle Front Pattern&amp;bull; Vee Neck&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Hand Wash Only&amp;bull; Updated Fit - Our most regular &amp;amp; modern fit&amp;nbsp;(see Size Guide below for more details and Euro/US conversion).&amp;nbsp;', '149.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_geelong_wool_argyle_vee_neck_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(934, 'B49G15', 'English Explorer', 'Mens English Explorer Wool Blend All Over Cable With Shawl Collar - Updated Fit', '&amp;nbsp;NEW FOR AUTUMN WINTER 2017&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;Inspired by traditional fisherman sweaters, this English Explorer cable-knit cardigan is a rustic choice for wintery days. It\'s crafted from a robust wool blend, has a shawl collar and fastens with chunky buttons.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 80% Wool | 20% Polyamide&amp;bull; All Over Cable&amp;bull; Shawl Collar&amp;bull; Machine Washable&amp;bull; Long Sleeve&amp;bull; Updated Fit - Our most regular &amp;amp; modern fit&amp;nbsp;(see Size Guide below for more details and Euro/US conversion).&amp;nbsp;', '149.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/e/n/english_explorer_mens_all_over_cable_with_shawl_collar.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(935, '101X54', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cashmere Crew Neck Jumper', 'This beautifully crafted jumper made from 100% pure cashmere will be a great addition to your wardrobe. Details include a classic crew neck, long sleeves and a regular fit. The use of the finest cashmere makes it an exquisite garment with an extra-soft finish. Minimal in color, it&amp;rsquo;s versatile when it comes to styling. &amp;nbsp;Perfect for pepping up your everyday wear or even as the centrepiece of an evening outfit, this stunning sweater is guaranteed to see you through Autumn / Winter season and beyond.', '178.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_cashmere_crew_neck_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(936, '101X55', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cashmere Roll Neck Jumper', 'This lightweight roll neck cashmere sweater is excellent for layering under our chunkier cashmere cardigans and capes. Crafted&amp;nbsp;from 100% pure cashmere&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;makes it an exquisite garment with an extra-soft finish. Minimal in color, it&amp;rsquo;s versatile when it comes to styling.', '184.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_cashmere_inset_sleeve_roll_neck_jumper_ecru_2_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(937, '101X56', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cashmere Crew Neck Cardigan', 'When it comes to your classic, crew-neck cardigan this season, go for luxurious-feeling,&amp;nbsp;afterall you deserve a little bit of luxury everyday. Beautifully crafted from a sumptuously soft cashmere for optimum comfort, this versatile design boasts long sleeves and a classic crew neckline. &amp;nbsp;', '184.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_cashmere_crew_neck_cardigan.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(938, '101X57', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Cashmere Short Sleeve Crew Neck Jumper', 'Soft to the touch and a flattering fit, this round neck short sleeve jumper is an everyday essential that will offer you&amp;nbsp;versatile styling options. Crafted from supersoft pure cashmere with short sleeves that are designed to create an exquisite slimming effect in the upper arms.', '169.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_cashmere_inset_short_sleeve_crew_neck_jumper_silver_2_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(939, '139X30', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Geelong Wool Crew Neck Cardigan', 'Soft to the touch and a flattering fit, this round neck cardigan is an everyday essential.&amp;nbsp;Crafted from supersoft geelong wool making this the&amp;nbsp;perfect wardrobe addition which can be worn with black trousers or skirt for a smarter look to jeans for a more casual feel.', '86.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_geelong_wool_crew_neck_cardigan.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(940, '139X49', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Geelong Wool Vee Neck Cardigan', 'With its neat fitted shape and easy flattering vee neck, this beautiful cardi works with everything. Beautifully crafted from supersoft geelong wool, it really merits a stunning new colour update, so take a look at our exquisite new season palette.', '86.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/1/_/1_139x49_rou_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(941, '139X52', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Geelong Wool Crew Neck Jumper', 'Complete your knitwear collection with this jumper; effortless to style from work to the weekend.&amp;nbsp;Soft to the touch and a flattering fit, this round neck long sleeve jumper is an everyday essential that will offer you&amp;nbsp;versatile styling options.&amp;nbsp;', '86.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/1/_/1_139x52_csk_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(942, '139X53', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Geelong Wool Roll Neck Jumper', 'Why not add this soft-feeling, pure geelong wool, roll-neck jumper to your cold-weather wardrobe this season? Not only is it warm and cosy, but it is also stylish and versatile, making it a great all-rounder!', '86.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_geelong_wool_roll_neck_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(943, '128D74', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Merino Wool Crew Neck Cardigan', 'Our ladies pure merino wool cardigan is perfect for throwing over a versatile number of outfits, making this is a new-season must have.&amp;nbsp;The body-temperature-adaptive, pure merino wool composition is great for keeping warm and cosy when it\'s chilly outside, and cool and comfortable when it\'s warmer.', '89.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/1/_/1_128d74_mlb_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(944, '128D76', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Merino Wool Vee Neck Jumper', 'A luxurious vee neck sweater is the ultimate foundation wardrobe piece for any woman. Our stylish sweater is crafted from the finest merino wool and is available in a number of striking colours. The ultimate finishing layer, the timeless appeal of this jumper will take you from season to season.', '89.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_merino_wool_vee_neck_jumper.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(945, '128D77', 'Womens > Womens Luxury Knitwear', 'Womens Merino Wool Roll Neck Jumper', 'Crafted from pure merino wool the jumper is soft to touch making it luxurious as well as comfortable. Fashioning a roll neck, the long sleeves feature a fine ribbed cuff.&amp;nbsp;', '89.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/w/o/womens_merino_wool_long_sleeve_roll_neck_jumper_chinati_2.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51');
