(946, 'RICUFEL', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Flat Caps & Hats', 'Richmond Unisex Felt Hat', '&amp;nbsp;Hurry, Limited Stock&amp;nbsp;Our Richmond Unisex Felt Hat is perfect for adding a touch of style to many of your favourite country looks this season and beyond! Crafted from 100% wool felt to offer you a stylish finish you are sure to love! This hat has been finished with a decorative leather band and feather detailing to offer you an added touch of style and wearability.&amp;nbsp;&amp;bull; 100% Wool Felt&amp;bull; Leather Decorative Band With Feather&amp;bull; Sizes shown are UK sizes (see size guide below for Euro/US conversion)', '44.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_richmond_unisex_felt_hat_in_navy_4.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(947, 'BERLBRK', 'Country Clothing > Ladies Country Clothing > Country Skirts & Trousers', 'Berwick Ladies Waterproof Breeks', 'Classically styled these soft-handled ladies tailored breeks are waterproof, breathable and fully lined for supreme comfort. Designed with flat fronted pleats for a flattering style with adjustable buckle at hem to achieve the perfect fit&amp;nbsp;and zipped pocket at the back.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/b/e/berwick_ladies_waterproof_breeks_olive_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(948, 'DURGBRK', 'Country Clothing > Mens Country Clothing > Country Breeks & Trousers', 'Dunswell Mens Waterproof Breeks', 'New this seasonn comes our men\'s waterproof shooting breeks. These&amp;nbsp;versatile breeks feature a buckle adjustable hem, 2 zip secure back pockets to protect your valuables &amp;amp; 2 hand side pockets.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/d/u/dunswell_mens_waterproof_shooting_breeks_9.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
