(954, 'COMGLBWX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Mens Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Lined Back Waistcoat Classic Fit - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! The Combrook Mens Tweed Waistcoat comes with action pleat back, designed for ease of movement. Available in a selection of country colours, this exquisite garment will certainly be a valued addition to any country wardrobe.Complete with a lined back, adjustable back strap, a ticket pocket and fully water repellent so no shock surprises when you are outdoors.&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_mens_lined-back_tweed_waistcoat_in_forest_green_2_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(955, 'COMLSHWX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Gilets & Waistcoats', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Shooting Waistcoat Classic Fit - Clearance Colour', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! New to our ladies Combrook range comes this classically designed technical ladies shooting waistcoat made from 100% pure wool tweed with a water repellent finish. This beautiful waistcoat features&amp;nbsp;with faux suede shoulder panels to aid gun mount and roomy cartridge pockets finished with a contrasting lining to compliment the tweed.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/c/o/combrook_ladies_tweed_shooting_waistcoat_in_meadow_7_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(956, '999H21', '', 'Mens Geelong Wool Crew Neck Jumper - Updated Fit - Web Exclusive', '&amp;nbsp;HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS EXTENDED!&amp;nbsp;Compared to Lambswool our Geelong jumpers are a lighter knit. The beauty of Geelong wool is that, despite the lightness, it gives a unique combination of warmth, softness and drape.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.&amp;nbsp;All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced.&amp;nbsp;', '120.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_geelong_wool_crew_neck_jumper_regalia_7_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(957, '999H20', '', 'Mens Geelong Wool Vee Neck Jumper - Updated Fit - Web Exclusive', '&amp;nbsp;HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS EXTENDED!&amp;nbsp;This jumper is crafted from a lighter weight pure geelong lambswool. All Alan Paine knitwear is fully fashioned; each garment is knitted to shape on the knitting machine and not cut and sewn.&amp;nbsp;Compared to Lambswool our Geelong jumpers are a lighter knit. The beauty of Geelong wool is that, despite the lightness, it gives a unique combination of warmth, softness and drape.Each sweater has three main component parts: back, front and sleeves. It is our skill in assembling these parts that is another mark of Alan Paine quality. Each stitch is linked by hand onto another to give the smoothest join possible.&amp;nbsp;All Alan Paine garments are finished by hand. The stress points of the garment &amp;ndash; under the arms, the cuffs and the ribs &amp;ndash; are all reinforced &amp;ndash; and the mitre of the &amp;ldquo;V&amp;rdquo; neck is closed by hand to give a perfect finish.', '120.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/m/e/mens_geelong_wool_vee_neck_jumper_regalia_7_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
