(959, 'COMLJACX', 'Sale - 1/2 Price Or Less > Ladies Sale > Country Collection', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Field Jacket - Shooting Fit - Clearance Colours', ' HURRY - SPECIAL PRICE ENDS SUNDAY! This super stylish waterproof field jacket is a new addition to the popular Combrook tweed range and the perfect choice for both town and country.With its pure wool, water repellent outer and designed to give you the perfect shooting fit, this jacket has all the functionality you&amp;rsquo;d expect from a shooting coat though it works just as well worn on a trip into town.&amp;nbsp;It has an array of useful pockets including two flap pockets, a secure map pocket under the front placket and a handy secure internal pocket.&amp;nbsp; The jacket also features a single back vent to aid movement and waterproof windbreaker cuffs to keep the cuff area snug against the body thus preventing gusts of wind rushing through the sleeve.&amp;nbsp;Available in a choice of stunning classic and contemporary tweed colourways this jacket is an absolute.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_ladies_field_jacket_in_meadow_10.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
