(962, 'LS1623-1', 'Mens > Polo Shirts', 'Men\'s Cotton Stretch Pique Polo Shirt With Tonal Undercollar With Crest', '&amp;nbsp;Summer Sale - Must End Soon&amp;nbsp;This short sleeve 3-button polo shirt is made from a 97% Cotton / 3% Elastic blend. The addition of elastic allows the shirt to stretch with the wearer whilst retaining its shape. The underside of the collar is a different contrasting colour on each colour shirt.', '44.00 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/l/s/ls1623_lbl_1_6.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
