(967, 'BERGCAP', 'Mens > Hats & Caps', 'Berwick Mens Waterproof Cap', 'Our new Berwick cap is fully waterproof, windproof and breathable for your all round comfort in the most testing of conditions.Designed in a traditional style, you are sure to love the classic feel of the waterproof Berwick Men\'s Flat Cap, ideal for pairing with your favourite Alan Paine shirt and trousers for those country pursuits or strolls around town. ', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_berwick_men_s_waterproof_cap_in_olive.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(968, 'FELGQUJ', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Felwell Mens Quilted Jacket - Classic Fit', 'Sure to offer warmth on those cooler days, the new men\'s Felwell Quilted Jacket is perfect for placing over your favourite Alan Paine sweater for an on-trend layered look. Crafted from a durable, yet luxurious quilted outer with an warm internal fleece for that extra bit of comfort. This jacket also features two-way centre front zipper with studded placket, fleeced-lined inner collar, two flap-secured bellow pockets &amp; stud adjustable side straps.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_felwell_mens_quilted_waistcoat_1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
