(970, 'HAPGJKT', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Hapton Men\'s Explorer Jacket - Classic Fit', 'The men\'s Hapton Waterproof Jacket is part of the Alan Paine English Explorer collection and offers you complete protection from the unpredictable weather when you are out and about. It includes a detachable hood, that can be folded away into the collar, to offer you total protection when the heavens open on your outdoor adventure. This outdoor jacket comes with two hand-warmer pockets, stud adjustable sleeve tabs &amp; two flap patch pockets with additional side entry pockets.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_hapton_mens_explorer_jacket_in_navy_1__1.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(971, 'FWG001', 'Mens > Shoes & Boots', 'Mens Leather Chelsea Ankle Boot', 'Coming Soon Beautifully constructed from 100% leather these new Alan Paine Chelsea Ankle Boots will become your new favourite fashion accessory for Autumn | Winter 2018.These boots feature a classic chisel square toe and flat heel with an durable rubber studded sole. Unique three layer insole including a thermal foil lining protecting feet from the cold and additional cushion padding in between lining &amp;amp; outer sole. Finished with red colour detail on the outer edge, Alan Paine crest embossed on the outer heel, inner lining &amp;amp; outer back edge.', '174.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_mens_leather_chelsea_ankle_boot_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(972, 'FWG002', 'Mens > Shoes & Boots', 'Men\'s Suede Chelsea Ankle Boot', 'Coming Soon These beautifully constructed boots are expertly crafted in supple brushed suede &amp;amp; leather making them versatile and a true complement to every ensemble.With a practical shallow heel, elegant rounded toe and signature Alan Paine crest on both the back edge, inner sole lining &amp;amp; sole this Chelsea boot is the wardrobe essential that will successfully see you through season-to-season.', '174.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_mens_suede_chelsea_ankle_boot.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
