(975, 'FWG005', 'Mens > Shoes & Boots', 'Men\'s Leather Waterproof Shooting Boot', 'Coming Soon Our new Men&amp;rsquo;s Leather Waterproof Shooting Boot offer you a mid-height performance hunting boot capable of taking on the harshest of conditions.These boots feature everything you would expect from an high-performing shooting boot, guaranteed waterproof and breathable, durable inject moulded bi-compound rubber outer sole, unique three layer insole including thermal foil lining to provide extra protection from the cold &amp;amp; complete with additional cushion padding to provide that extra bit of comfort.', '209.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_men_s_leather_waterproof_tall_boot_1__8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
