(977, 'FWL007', 'Womens > Boots & Shoes', 'Ladies Leather & Tweed Waterproof Shooting Boot', 'Coming Soon Ladies Leather &amp;amp; Tweed Waterproof Shooting Boot is a classic looking lightweight and robust leather, with tweed detail boot developed for the female shooter. Using a waterproof with breathable comfort membrane, excellent heel stability and flexible forefoot &amp;amp; wool-lined foot for added comfort and warmth as the colder days draw in. Finished with a lace up front for added comfort, as well as Alan Paine branding to the front tongue for added style and wearability, these boots will carry through this season and beyond with ease.', '179.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_ladies_leather_tweed_waterproof_boot.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(978, 'FWL008', 'Womens > Boots & Shoes', 'Ladies Leather Tall Waterproof Country Boot', 'Coming Soon The Alan Paine Ladies Country Boots are perfect for enjoying country living, offering a stylish waterproof and breathable boot you are sure to love!These boots are the perfect companion come rain or shine this season and beyond. The waterproof &amp;amp; breathable leather outer is ideal for offering you added comfort and wearability, drying out quickly after getting caught out in those unpredictable showers. The adjustable buckle fastening offers you a secure and sure fit, keeping you comfortable whilst on the move. Complete with excellent heel stability and flexible forefoot &amp;amp; wool-lined foot for added comfort and warmth as the colder days draw in. Finished with a tweed detail around the top inner lining, as well as Alan Paine branding crest embossed on the outer back edge for added style and wearability, these boots will carry through this season and beyond with ease.', '234.95 GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_ladies_leather_tall_waterproof_boot.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
