(980, 'COMGCOT-1', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Combrook Mens Waterproof Tweed Shooting Coat - Shooting Fit', 'New Woodland Tweed ColourwayThe Combrook Mens Shooting Coat has been part of our product offering since the launch of the country collection and continues to be one of the most popular garments in the Combrook range.Engineered with a 100% wool water repellent outer, this robust and hardwearing garment is armed with a waterproof &amp;amp; breathable membrane to keep you comfortable in the most testing of weather conditions. Insulated with a soft polyester wadding alongside deep manly hand warmer pockets and storm cuffs, all to keep you warm on those cold wintery mornings.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_men_s_coat_in_sage_8.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(981, 'COMGBLR', 'Mens > Jackets & Coats', 'Combrook Mens Tweed Blazer - Classic Fit', 'New Woodland Tweed ColourwayIf the occasion calls for something smart then our Combrook Mens Tweed Blazer with its 100% water repellent outer certainly ‘fits the bill’.Superbly tailored with a 3 button front closure, double back vents, ticket pocket, two internal pockets along with its contrast lining tonal with the tweed over check to complete the look. This exquisite garment will certainly be a valued addition to any wardrobe.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_mens_tweed_blazer_in_lagoon_1__7.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
(982, 'COMLBRE', 'Combrook Collection > Combrook Ladies', 'Combrook Ladies Tweed Breeks', 'New for Autumn | Winter 2018 are these very flattering pair of ladies tweed breeks made from a soft rich blend of pure wool tweed for a naturally hard-wearing warm pair of country breeks.Available on their own or with matching waistcoat, jacket and hats if you are looking for a full tweed ladies shooting suit.', ' GBP', 'https://www.alanpaine.co.uk/media/catalog/product/a/l/alan_paine_combrook_ladies_breeks_in_juniper_10.jpg', '2018-08-14 13:45:51', '2018-08-14 13:45:51'),
